Network Notifier
----------------

The main purpose of this program is to send and receive network notifications in a LAN.

It uses an UDP socket on port 7415 to receive broadcast messages (sent to 224.0.0.1) in an XML format with a SHA-256 hash to guarantee the message integrity.

Python scripts are already tested and working, Android app is currently under development (alpha state).

Published under GPL-v3 license.
